item_category: Purpose-built to catapult you into the world of gaming and esports, this formidable tower will burst your productivity and creativity options wide open. The Lenovo IdeaCentre Gaming 5i is available with Intel Core processor, NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1650 discrete graphics GPU, 8 GB DDR4 memory, and storage options encased in a refracting Chameleon Blue compact configuration.
